fields.query:
select 
	"SERVICE"."SERVICE_ID",
	"SERVICE_T"."CITY"
from 
	"SERVICE"
left join "SERVICE_T" 
	on "SERVICE"."SERVICE_ID" = "SERVICE_T"."SERVICE_ID" 
	and "SERVICE_T"."LANGUAGE" = '[LANGUAGE]'
join "SERVICE_GROUP" 
	on "SERVICE"."SERVICE_GROUP_ID" = "SERVICE_GROUP"."SERVICE_GROUP_ID" 
	and "SERVICE_GROUP"."SERVICE_GROUP_ID" = 2 -- only "Leitbehörde Gemeinde"
where
	"SERVICE"."DISABLED" = 0
	and "SERVICE"."SERVICE_PARENT_ID" is null;

fields.query:
select 
	"SERVICE"."SERVICE_ID",
	"SERVICE_T"."NAME" 
from 
	"SERVICE"
left join "SERVICE_T" 
	on "SERVICE"."SERVICE_ID" = "SERVICE_T"."SERVICE_ID" 
	and "SERVICE_T"."LANGUAGE" = '[LANGUAGE]'
join "SERVICE_GROUP" 
	on "SERVICE"."SERVICE_GROUP_ID" = "SERVICE_GROUP"."SERVICE_GROUP_ID"
where
	"SERVICE"."DISABLED" = 0
union
	select '-1', 'Andere'
order by 2
